<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Les étudiants étrangers peuvent-ils obtenir un permis de séjour ?</h3>
<p>Oui, les étudiants étrangers inscrits dans une université en Turquie peuvent demander un permis de séjour étudiant en présentant leurs documents d&#8217;inscription scolaire.</p></p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-04-17T04:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-14T15:47:10Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/international-students-in-turkey.webp","alt":"Social life for international students studying at universities in Turkey.","title":"international-students-in-turkey"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'fr' AND "slug" = 'permis-de-travail-pour-les-etudiants-internationaux-en-turquie' );
