</ul>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="enjoy-your-stay-with-good-manners">Enjoy your stay with good manners!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">When you are invited to Turkish homes, following the rules of etiquette makes both you and your host feel comfortable. Hospitality is an important part of Turkish culture and by following these rules, you can better understand and experience this culture. Remember, every new experience can give your life a new direction. To experience the warmth and hospitality of Turkish families, consider invitations and pay attention to these rules.</p>



