<h2 id="turkiyede-cv-ve-ozgecmisin-onemi-yurt-disinda-egitim-alan-ogrenciler-icin-neden-gereklidir" class="wp-block-heading">L&#8217;importance du CV en Turquie : Pourquoi est-ce nécessaire ?</h2>
<article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" tabindex="-1" data-turn-id="request-WEB:8a068d7c-4944-4232-86b5-00f922974ed7-7" data-testid="conversation-turn-16" data-scroll-anchor="true" data-turn="assistant">
